{"tid":1269753,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"最近死嘅烈士，令我諗起哩隻歌","createTime":"2019-06-30T16:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T03:28:49.000Z","uid":132544,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d917a390644fa6ca73ad7dd8ee47769150989814","tid":1269753,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"相信有玩過metal gear 嘅朋友，都會聽過哩首歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7oday_Fc-Gc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7oday_Fc-Gc&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=f280d74d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7oday_Fc-Gc</a><br />\n<br />\n其實哩隻歌有段故嘅<br />\n<br />\n事情發生係1920年，<br />\n當時美國社會普遍歧視意利人，<br />\n歌入面提及嘅Nicola and Bart係麻省造鞋工廠嘅<br />\n意大利裔員工嚟，<br />\n佢地捲入一單造鞋工廠嘅槍殺案，<br />\n雖後來證實彈道不符，<br />\n兩人更有不在場證據，<br />\n但當地法庭卻咬定其無政府主義，<br />\n堅持兩人有罪。<br />\n最終係1921年Nicola 同 Bart 被一級殺人罪起訴。<br />\n雖然各地都有示威抗議，<br />\n認為判決在違人權，<br />\n但係1927年8月23日，<br />\nNicola 同Bart 因無理嘅控罪，<br />\n因政見及種族，<br />\n被判死刑，<br />\n各地譁然<br />\n和平示威亦變成咗暴動，<br />\n只為Nicola 同 Bart爭取公道。<br />\n五十六年後，麻省政府終於係1977年聲明，<br />\n兩人並無罪嫌，<br />\n哩份公義，足足遲咗五十六年。<br />\n<br />\n或者如同skull所講，<br />\nYour favorite song. Nicola. Bart. <br />\nImmigrants, wrongly executed. <br />\nBut their deaths served as a message to others. That ours is a society that murders the innocent. Do you, too, believe your sacrifice will change the world?<br />\n<br />\n我希望烈士嘅犧牲，能如Nicola 同Bart一樣，<br />\n為香港甚至世界作出改變，<br />\n多謝你地。"},{"pid":"eca0ab0018a24076aee3cc692620c56be036ae83","tid":1269753,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:10:14.000Z","msg":"補返source先<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=486&amp;snB=112221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FCo.php%3Fbsn%3D486%26snB%3D112221&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=c3684014\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=486&amp;snB=112221</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Here%27s_to_You_(song)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHere%2527s_to_You_%28song%29&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=fb154366\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Here%27s_to_You_(song)</a>"},{"pid":"78b73e91140d366d597f460030d9af9d079cc2d1","tid":1269753,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:15:36.000Z","msg":"哩首歌好有意義，希望大家都可推廣比朋友聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc98fee44e89ee3290e30ebb45efed0b16092839","tid":1269753,"uid":271064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"da19d3582281ca264a474503843221979fd4456c","tid":1269753,"uid":259700,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c6f36f88c40611de28db71a8eda4922c9aab6f9","tid":1269753,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"da19d3582281ca264a474503843221979fd4456c","tid":1269753,"uid":259700,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"我相信John Lennon仲在生，<br />\n佢一定會企係我地哩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6702fd82803b89e5e29c36e67c5f79b000ca9f8","tid":1269753,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pEBSp-fkNog/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FpEBSp-fkNog%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=aadd47d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e01543873885f91268a9bfabc05d8ec754906a2","tid":1269753,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:25:19.0